{
  "stem": "25639.11",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I fell deeply in love [LAUGHS] that evening.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was afraid nothing will come of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And but I moved out to Los Angeles when my aunt decided to stay there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, since I resided with her in Kansas City, and she brought me out here, it was a natural transition.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I looked forward to living in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, I was closer to San Francisco, where someone I loved was going to law school, in San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I was hoping that perhaps this will nurture the relationship.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That summer, we corresponded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I didn't speak English, but I was learning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Consequently, every letter-- every word in each letter was looked up in a dictionary.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "However, the sentences and the sentence structure is quite chaotic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And now we can laugh about it when we look at those letters 47-plus years later.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Indeed I saw Karl, and we got engaged in January of 1949.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And on August 17th, when he had a school break after his second year of law school, we married in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And immediately, we-- well, we flew up to the Santa Cruz mountains, where we had our honeymoon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I moved to San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Karl is-- was born in Germany in Ba-- in Buhl, in the state of Baden, near, near Baden-Baden, in southern Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1937, he, he fled Nazi Germany when it no longer was safe for him there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His parents thought that he has no future there, and this is the right move.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at-- so at age 15, he went to Kansas City, Missouri, where his uncle lived, his father's brother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Karl left behind his father, Alfred Lyon, and his mother, Joan Lyon.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
